You can place this soft and rounded finger toothbrush on your index finger and gently massage your baby’s gums to relieve the pain that is caused during teething. The Stimulator is meant to be used when you get the first glimpses of those pearly whites. The soft and soothing Stimulator help clean the teeth when they begin to emerge and it massages the gums to offer relieving comfort. The Stimulator is easy to clean and easy to use.

The Toddler Toothbrush is a brush that is used when your baby’s teeth have fully emerged. the toothbrush has an ergonomic design that makes it easy to clean your baby’s teeth. The soft bristles are gentle on your baby’s sensitive teeth and gums. Brush your baby’s teeth with a dampened toothbrush to ensure maximum comfort. The toothbrush is easy to use and easy to clean before and after use.

This comprehensive oral care set from MeeMee has all the essential items that can help you get your baby on a thorough oral hygiene regimen. This pediatrician approved oral care set is made from non-toxic materials assuring maximum hygiene and safety for your little one.
